#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.ogrid.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.ogrid"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:1 of
msgid "Construct a multi-dimensional \"meshgrid\"."
msgstr "构造一个多维的“网格”。"

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:3 of
msgid ""
"``grid = nd_grid()`` creates an instance which will return a mesh-grid "
"when indexed.  The dimension and number of the output arrays are equal to"
" the number of indexing dimensions.  If the step length is not a complex "
"number, then the stop is not inclusive."
msgstr ""
"``grid = nd_grid()`` 创建一个实例，当被索引时会返回一个网格。输出数组的"
"维度和数量等于索引维度的数量。如果步长不是一个复数，则终点不包含在内。"

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:8 of
msgid ""
"However, if the step length is a **complex number** (e.g. 5j), then the "
"integer part of its magnitude is interpreted as specifying the number of "
"points to create between the start and stop values, where the stop value "
"**is inclusive**."
msgstr ""
"然而，如果步长是一个**复数**（例如 5j），则其大小的整数部分被解释为指定在"
"起始值和终止值之间创建的点的数量，其中终止值**是包含在内的**。"

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:13 of
msgid ""
"If instantiated with an argument of ``sparse=True``, the mesh-grid is "
"open (or not fleshed out) so that only one-dimension of each returned "
"argument is greater than 1."
msgstr ""
"如果使用参数 ``sparse=True`` 实例化，则网格是开放的（或未完全展开的），"
"因此每个返回参数中只有一个维度大于1。"

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:17 of
msgid "Whether the grid is sparse or not. Default is False."
msgstr "网格是否为稀疏格式。默认为 False。"

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:21 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:22 of
msgid ""
"Two instances of `nd_grid` are made available in the maxframe.tensor "
"namespace, `mgrid` and `ogrid`::"
msgstr ""
"在 maxframe.tensor 命名空间中提供了两个 `nd_grid` 的实例：`mgrid` 和 `"
"ogrid`："

#: ../../docstring maxframe.tensor.ogrid:28 of
msgid ""
"Users should use these pre-defined instances instead of using `nd_grid` "
"directly."
msgstr "用户应使用这些预定义的实例，而不是直接使用 `nd_grid`。"

